This notebook was made for the competition (https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/prometeo23-kaggle/overview/about-prometeo23) hosted bu IIT Jodhpur in Feb 2023.
Problem statement:  Given a text and a "phrase" from it, you are tasked to detect the sentiment expressed towards the "phrase" in the text instance among 
the following categories: positive, neutral and negative.
I was able to get an accuracy of 74.8% which got my team a position in top ten in the competition.
